    "body": "Se we can hide, but inevitably if enough time passes it will start breaking as we add & test new features only on compact mode.\r\nremoving it does simplify the code a lot but then re-adding then will be a lot of work\r\n\r\nso the options are:\r\n\r\n* keep it as it is, with compact mode as default\r\n* hide the chat mode option, with compact mode as default BUT => **with the intention in the short term to bring it back** <=\r\n* remove chat mode completely & forever, hold a funeral (or a party)\r\n\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n@simonricoo compact mode is/was already the default.",
